context_17609=The Beggar's Sect is in chaos after a failed assassination attempt. Take Elder Lu's token. Find out which disciples were wounded, and get the appropriate medicine from Xia Laishun, the manager.   <br>Giving up this task will be treated as giving up the trial. <br>Omniscient Scholar Memorandum: <br><s>Accept the task and get three Elder Orders. Choose three wounded disciples out of six to cure with appropriate antidotes. With Elder Order 1, you can talk to He Yiliu (519, 300) or You Genzi (611, 373). With Elder Order 2, you can talk to Jing Xiao (618, 355) or Man Dan (631, 331). With Elder Order 3, you can talk to Bao Yu (610, 378) or Yin Chuo (610, 379). <br><s>The six wounded disciples' antidotes are Qingge Powder, Hanzhang Pill, Ruyi Pill, Hongqiu Pill, Huaye Powder and Qinye Pill respectively. Find Xia Laishun, Beggar's Sect Warehouse Manager (637, 373). Get appropriate antidotes from him. <br><s>Talk to the three disciples you choose to cure. And then submit the task to Xiao Tianfang (554, 335).
