context_17612=Elder Lu asked you to find Sect Leader Xiao Tianfang. Sect Leader seems to want to go to Tangmen, thus he asked you to accompany him. <br>Giving up this task will be treated as giving up the trial. <br>Omniscient Scholar Memorandum: <br><s>This task gives the item Elder Lu Order 2. Talk with Xiao Tianfang (554, 335). He requests you to go to Tangmen. <br><s>When you arrive at Tangmen, talk with Beggars' Sect Disciple Zhu Di (674, 135). And then go to the woods (699, 93) behind him. The animation is played. <br><s>When the animation ends, talk with Xiao Tianfang, and he will lead you to Tangmen. Follow him and kill everyone on your way. When you arrive in drawbridge, the task will be completed and the animation will play. <br><s>When the animation ends, Xiao Tianfang will ask you to visit Zhu Di. Return to Zhu Di (674, 135) at Tang Family Castle's Stagecoach and finish task to get Leader's Token. <br><s>In the end, return to Beggars' Sect to talk with Lu Shufang (556, 298) to complete the task.

